'''邵陽字牌'''，是流傳於[[湖南|湖南]][[邵陽縣|邵陽縣]]的[[字牌|字牌]]遊戲<ref name="邵阳字牌">{{Cite news|url=http://www.52baxi.cn/GameRules.aspx?KindID=613|title=邵阳字牌|language=zh-cn|publisher=邵阳八喜棋牌游戏官方网站|author=|date=|accessdate=2013-09-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111114021/http://www.52baxi.cn/GameRules.aspx?KindID=613|archivedate=2014-01-11}}</ref>。當地還有稱為'''剝皮胡'''的玩法，差別只在数醒者能得到胡牌者一半胡數，胡數多者扣除胡數少者的胡數<ref name="剝皮胡">{{Cite news|url=http://www.52baxi.cn/GameRules.aspx?KindID=624|title=剝皮胡|language=zh-cn|publisher=邵阳八喜棋牌游戏官方网站|author=|date=|accessdate=2013-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111110652/http://www.52baxi.cn/GameRules.aspx?KindID=624|archive-date=2014-01-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="从“三打哈 ”到“剥皮”">{{Cite news|url=http://news.shaoyangnews.net/shiping/2011/04/19598.shtml|title=从“三打哈 ”到“剥皮”|language=zh-cn|publisher=邵阳晚報|author=欧阳升|date=2009-11-19|accessdate=2013-09-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111110532/http://news.shaoyangnews.net/shiping/2011/04/19598.shtml|archivedate=2014-01-11}}</ref>。

==牌具==
